Translation Architecture Analysis
Objective

The platform explored future bilingual support.

Languages:

Arabic
English
Translation Approaches Evaluated
Approach 1

Manual text replacement

Result:

Rejected

Reason:

Poor scalability

Approach 2

Translation dictionary

Result:

Accepted as future lightweight solution

Example:

{
login: {
ar: "تسجيل الدخول",
en: "Login"
}
}
Approach 3

Full i18n system

Result:

Postponed

Reason:

The platform UI is still evolving.

Implementing translation before UI completion would create unnecessary maintenance overhead.

